      "message": "SGTM.\n\nI believe it\u0027s permanent. There\u0027s also no \"..\", though that\u0027s emulated in various places to make it seem like there sort of is.\n\nI\u0027m only passingly familiar, but I think the main motivation is sandboxing, in that it means that a handle to a directory can be the root of a view into a tree, without any way to escape to a higher level or elsewhere on the filesystem.",
